www.mojidict.com/</a><br />\nhjdict jp <a href=\"https://dict.hjenglish.com/jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdict.hjenglish.com%2Fjp%2F&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=c2874116\" target=\"_blank\">https://dict.hjenglish.com/jp/</a>"},{"pid":"190b7f2916ba2204ef0b3103846469cfe30fb07a","tid":1495199,"uid":133277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"報N5先啦<br />\n<br />\n我之前都係讀咗N5一年 之後連自學都冇 <br />\n淨係睇下日本綜藝聽下日文歌 <br />\n上年膽粗粗報咗N2 最尾合格咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得N5真係基本功唔可以miss<br />\n之後可以揀自學定keep住學<br />\n不過自學就好少機會訓練到說同寫<br />\n所以我而家說寫都仲係N5程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e6a5184cd360c7b2fa5ea4277873e79363f2ce","tid":1495199,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22241b32cff2149d05e1291a493f34c87cb4e989","tid":1495199,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"想去學日文<br />\n新手🙏🏻<br />\n想請教巴打們 有冇咩學校好推介同課程介紹<br />\n一開始入手報N4定5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"想學到咩程度,用途?"},{"pid":"05a328cd2fc81dda17bf2c6bc3ef719a1fc32904","tid":1495199,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e6a5184cd360c7b2fa5ea4277873e79363f2ce","tid":1495199,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22241b32cff2149d05e1291a493f34c87cb4e989","tid":1495199,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"想去學日文<br />\n新手🙏🏻<br />\n想請教巴打們 有冇咩學校好推介同課程介紹<br />\n一開始入手報N4定5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"想學到咩程度,用途?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"想學到去 聽得明日本人講咩"},{"pid":"f4769dc6aed3745aad8d3569c7120390b215bce3","tid":1495199,"uid":293963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"我係自學🙈<br />\n中學個陣對日文幾有興趣<br />\n自己背完五十音之後係咁睇日文karaoke<br />\n再自己買本大家的日本語+上youtube學<br />\n學左幾年 當初冇諗住要考，個陣搵工先諗住考張cert<br />\n結果直接輕鬆考到N2😂"},{"pid":"e7c000104c8956cce7cd04f187e5edcec12e58db","tid":1495199,"uid":284038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"Google 日文 自學<br />\n背曬50音先<br />\n明曬prep例如は が を へ に で の之類, 務求睇得明簡單句子<br />\n然後你會開始去理解複雜啲嘅嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得睇動畫睇劇聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7f24ae44212214fae7c44dac9ecd556aa4c17c","tid":1495199,"uid":281584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05a328cd2fc81dda17bf2c6bc3ef719a1fc32904","tid":1495199,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e6a5184cd360c7b2fa5ea4277873e79363f2ce","tid":1495199,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22241b32cff2149d05e1291a493f34c87cb4e989","tid":1495199,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"想去學日文<br />\n新手🙏🏻<br />\n想請教巴打們 有冇咩學校好推介同課程介紹<br />\n一開始入手報N4定5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"想學到咩程度,用途?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"想學到去 聽得明日本人講咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:15:11.000Z","msg":"日本人講野都分好多層次<br />\n我攞到N1聽得明先生同我講咩,因為佢為就我,知我係外國人,用返教過嘅日文<br />\n但係日本返工個陣,同事老細講d日文好多係無教過,好多野有要學過<br />\n包括術語,更難係d口語加話中有話,而自己好難用返佢地果套答返<br />\n唔同年紀,教育程度,用字同表達都有分别<br />\n如果係旅行睇動漫,係香港點學都好,考到N2都夠<br />\n如果想聽得明絕大部分日本人真係講d咩,要係日本返工先得,就算係日本讀日文,都唔係真係當你日本人咁講野"},{"pid":"542b4466d80fdb533f458eb8ecd121e9cb82fa2c","tid":1495199,"uid":254547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4769dc6aed3745aad8d3569c7120390b215bce3","tid":1495199,"uid":293963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"我係自學🙈<br />\n中學個陣對日文幾有興趣<br />\n自己背完五十音之後係咁睇日文karaoke<br />\n再自己買本大家的日本語+上youtube學<br />\n學左幾年 當初冇諗住要考，個陣搵工先諗住考張cert<br />\n結果直接輕鬆考到N2😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:57:49.000Z